spec_data.Name: openssl-static
spec_data.Description:
OpenSSL is a toolkit for supporting cryptography. The openssl-static
package contains static libraries needed for static linking of
applications which support various cryptographic algorithms and
protocols.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 04 Aug 2017 11:01:56 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Libraries for static linking of applications which will use OpenSSL
